message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper deals with the application of 3D fully convolutional networks for multi-organ segmentation in CT scans. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) categories. Additionally, since the paper deals with medical imaging, it could also belong to the medical imaging (cs.MED) category. Finally, since the paper uses neural networks for segmentation, it could also belong to the neural networks (cs.NEURON) category.
